2 Welcome to Group 2’s Booklet
This book is dedicated to showcasing the work of Group 2, a dynamic team of dedicated students from the Visualization class at the prestigious Oral Roberts University, Oklahoma, under the guidance of Dr. V. Here, you’ll find weekly Quarto documents and exciting projects as they explore the world of data visualization.
